               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary>An incomplete copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Toṉṉūl Viḷakkam</title> by Beschi. It starts with the prose commentary on <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign> 39 (U2, f23r1) and ends with the commentary on <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign> 200 (U2, f137v8), that is, the bundle starts with the last page of the <title xml:lang="ta">Collatikāram</title> and ends with the last page of the <title xml:lang="ta">Poruḷatikāram</title>.
                    </summary>
                  
